reviewText: Good games, but they had better.

Scarce are the years of Greatness for the ol Jettys. A Super Bowl in 1969 and the 2009 Season of playoffs. THis dvd captures that year perfectly, showcasing three great wins of the 2009 season. They are the Jets vs Patriots week 2, Jets vs The Bengals in the afc Wilcard game and last the awesome win over San Diego in the AFC Divisional playoff game. Very well narrated! A 3 Disc set that any Jets fan will surely enjoy.
This is the best dvd ever for my husband he loves it more every day. Wish I had gotten it sooner.

Here are three games from the 2009 season. The one that stands out is the beating we gave New England. Brady just could not throw he was under such pressure from the Jets Defense.

Also included are the regular season games with Cincinnatti and San Diego, games where the team really played well.
I was very disappointed when I received this DVD. The games have been edited, so you miss out on the chat between plays, effectively killing the flow and atmosphere of the games.
